OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. A risk of a rural grass
OL,9,Ffrost across eastern counties. Mostly
OL,10,Flight winds, but breezier across the
OL,11,Ffar wets of Cornwall and the Isles of
OL,12,FScilly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy light rain
OL,15,Farriving across the region from late
OL,16,Fmorning. Some places remaining dry
OL,17,Fbefore skies break and sunny spells
OL,18,Fdevelop into the afternoon. Becoming
OL,19,Frather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
